nt this information is not provided pursuant to subparagraph (B). The specific actions shall not supersede the provisions of existing local collective bargaining agreements within the jurisdiction of the county superintendent of schools.</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(2) Commencing with the 2019–20 fiscal year and in each fiscal year thereafter, the county
